room_title: Escape room "Bank Robbery Escape" by Master Escape Room in Miami
room_address: 1700 North Dixie Hwy, Boca Raton, FL 33432
room_description: Today you have a chance to commit the robbery of the century. The most important bank will be updating their security system, and the alarms will be down for 55 minutes. The general response time from the police will give you five more minutes to escape, but that's it. How much money can you steal?
